name: Ian Maher
bio: Ian Maher graduated from General Assembly in 2023. I am a creative and process-driven full stack software developer with enthusiasm for building accessible designs and constructing technical solutions with the user in mind. I apply my professional experience as an educator and guidance counselor to my present work, with a focus on communication and an ability to work with people of all backgrounds. I thrive in a collaborative environment and am enthusiastic about projects centered on learning and inclusion.
